  "googleSignInCanceledBody": "A “canceled” error usually means OAuth misconfiguration, not that you tapped cancel. In Google Cloud Console: 1) Android OAuth client with your app package and the SHA-1 of the keystore for this build (from the android folder: gradlew signingReport). 2) GOOGLE_SERVER_CLIENT_ID must be your Web client ID from the same project. 3) Optional: GOOGLE_ANDROID_CLIENT_ID with the Android client ID in your build defines. If you ship via Play, also add Play App Signing’s SHA-1.",
